{{see|kısmet}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From the Turkish ''[[kısmet]]'', from Arabic ''{{ARchar|[[قسمة|قِسْمَة]]}}'' "fate".

===Noun===
'''kismet'''

# [[fate]], [[fortune]], [[destiny]]

